BEGIN_PGML

>> #### Practice #### <<

1. Find the sum of the first  [`[$n[0]]`] terms in this sequence: [`[$disp[0]] \dots`].  
    a. What is the first term of this sum? [__________]{$seq[0][0]}
    b. What is the [`[$n[0]]^{[$th[0]]}`] term of the sum? [___________]{$last[0]}
