\color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]} &|& \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]} &|& \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]} &|&  &|& \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]} &|& \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]} &|& \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]}  \\
\end{array}`] <<

The sum of each pair is [`\color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]}`].

(d) The sum of the first [`\color{brown}{[$n[0]]}`] terms is
>> [` \dfrac{\color{brown}{[$n[0]]}\cdot \color{darkcyan}{[$pair[0]]}}{2} =  [$sum[0]].`]<<

